transArray.content: The reserved room has a superior king-size bed. Each room has a tea cabinet, a fat blue milk cup, free coffee and tea bags, and a bag of each tea type is very considerate. There is a small park to the east of the hotel where you can go jogging if you get up early! !

Dear family, your satisfaction is refreshing because of the spring breeze and Buddha's face. Because of your satisfaction, we have the motivation to make unremitting efforts and make us make more progress!
